## Getting started

Open `experiment.yaml` and fill in every field marked with `~` (STEP 1 in the file).
Then run:

```bash
sforge validate --config ./experiment.yaml
sforge generate --config ./experiment.yaml --dry_run
sforge generate --config ./experiment.yaml
```

Submit the generated Slurm scripts under `runs/.../batch_*/sbatch/`.

